Particleboard and medium-density fiberboard production, imports,

Dataset containing various statistics for particleboard and medium-density fiberboard. All units are in Million Square ft unless otherwise specified.

howard53

Format

A data frame with 56 observations of 7 variables

Source

National Particleboard Association (20); U.S. International Trade Commission (69); U.S. Department of Agriculture (32). Data may not add to totals because of rounding.

Details

  • Prod.Tot Total Particleboard and Medium-Density Fiberboard Production
  • Prod.ParticleBoard Particleboard Production
  • Prod.MediumDensityFiberboard Medium-Density Fiberboard Production
  • Imports Particleboard and Medium-Density Fiberboard Imports
  • Exports Particleboard and Medium-Density Fiberboard Exports
  • Consump.Tot Total Particleboard and Medium-Density Fiberboard Consumption
  • Consump.PerCap(Sq ft) Per Capita Consumption, in Square ft.
